OL,3,CJersey's Council of Ministers meeting
OL,4,Cto discuss ferry dilemma
OL,6,F"We have sought answers to these
OL,7,Fquestions throughout the process and
OL,8,Fthe Council of Ministers is pleased to
OL,9,Fhave received some clarity over the
OL,10,Fpast 24 hours to validate the concerns
OL,11,Fof the Minister for Sustainable
OL,12,FEconomic Development.
OL,14,F"We are now considering the answers
OL,15,Fand will make a further announcement
OL,16,Fon Monday."
OL,18,FGuernsey made the shock announcement
OL,19,Fon Wednesday that it would be picking
OL,20,FCondor, owned by Brittany Ferries.
