OL,3,CJersey's Council of Ministers meeting
OL,4,Cto discuss ferry dilemma
OL,6,FHowever, Jersey's Economic Development
OL,7,FMinister says this does not mean the
OL,8,Fisland will not be rushed into making
OL,9,Fits own decision.
OL,11,FSpeaking to ITV Channel, Deputy
OL,12,FKirsten Morel, said: "We're not at the
OL,13,Fposition of going with two operators.
OL,14,FWe're at the position where Jersey
OL,15,Fwants and needs more information from
OL,16,Fboth operators to ensure things such
OL,17,Fas financial stability.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
