OL,3,CJersey's Council of Ministers meeting
OL,4,Cto discuss ferry dilemma
OL,6,F"We need to make sure we chose a
OL,7,Fprovider who can provide services for
OL,8,Fthe full 15 years. We don't want
OL,9,FJersey or Guernsey tax payers to be in
OL,10,Fa position where they are forced into
OL,11,Fsome rescue packages."
OL,13,FIt comes amid reports that Condor
OL,14,Fasked the government for a loan of
OL,15,F#80M in the last year, with #10M
OL,16,Fneeded up front to secure their
OL,17,Fservices. This was allegedly rejected
OL,18,Fat the time.
OL,20,FWatch the full interview here...
