OL,3,CJersey's Council of Ministers meeting
OL,4,Cto discuss ferry dilemma
OL,6,FWhen asked if he would pursue another
OL,7,Foperator if he can't get a guarantee
OL,8,Fthat Jersey taxpayers will not be
OL,9,Fresponsible for picking up a potential
OL,10,Frescue deal, he replied: "There's
OL,11,Flogic in that but not something I'm
OL,12,Fwilling to say at the moment."
OL,14,FDeputy Morel also added: "I'm not
OL,15,Fgoing to be pulled at the minute one
OL,16,Fway or the other (with who Jersey will
OL,17,Fselect). What I want to make sure is
OL,18,Fwhoever we appoint that they have the
OL,19,Ffinancial stability to last that 15
OL,20,Fyears, that really is for me the
OL,21,Fbottom line."
